title: Was FunnyMike arrested? Viral rumor accuses YouTuber of new murder charge as truth finally comes out
summary_full: A viral post falsely claimed YouTuber FunnyMike was arrested for murder in 2026. The claim came from a parody account and had no police or media support. FunnyMike is free and active online. His only real murder charge was in 2016, and the case was suspended in 2017 due to lack of evidence.
